{"tid":2192211,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"湯家驊：以言入罪非違反人權　法庭會平衡","createTime":"2020-09-07T03:35:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T04:09:48.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bc392e4d9c68daf2bdefa3d301a7fa351bd67a59","tid":2192211,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T03:35:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548234-20200907.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548234-20200907.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNp4T2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=e5b84c97\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548234-20200907.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=8d69be31\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548234-20200907.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n人民力量副主席譚得志昨日以《刑事罪行條例》第10條被警方國安處拘捕，他涉嫌發表煽動文字，涉及他在街站及社交媒體直播的內容。<br />\n<br />\n行政會議成員、資深大律師湯家驊在本台節目《千禧年代》表示，對於有評論指有關案件是「以言入罪」、「文字獄」，湯家驊認為以言入罪並非違反人權，《國際人權公約》亦指，言論有機會受法律限制，亦可以構成刑事罪行，單單指言論不應有法律規管是不正確，法庭會做平衡，衡量限制與個人自由是否對稱，認為有關罪行未必視為違反人權或違憲，由於在普通法下，並無引用過相關法例，要給予法庭空間去凝聚法律原則。<br />\n<br />\n至於狠批政府的言論，會否違反有關條例，湯家驊認為，製造仇恨與「罵得狠」有分別，相信一般人均明白，例如「黑警死全家」涉及仇恨，「林鄭落台」則未必，相信無可能分析每個情況。<br />\n<br />\n他認為，與有關條文最相近的是刑事藐視法庭，相信如要構成憎恨政府，是要證明有多大機會令社會廣泛憎恨政府的情況出現，法庭會從各種不同背景、環境證據作決定。"},{"pid":"189fe12a64c26d407664d8d87ac962c095bd35a6","tid":2192211,"uid":116289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T03:36:12.000Z","msg":"淚"},{"pid":"314b7c5db4735594d63f0649af03afbdb2be99bd","tid":2192211,"uid":272652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T03:37:00.000Z","msg":"灑"},{"pid":"371bea9fd3326ec5ecd4b51eef111637f3d98784","tid":2192211,"uid":67346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T03:37:33.000Z","msg":"雪"},{"pid":"1443b4baf994f677176f498cad54eedcbbece7c6","tid":2192211,"uid":310968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T03:40:17.000Z","msg":"廠"},{"pid":"f9f6aa19c0d4fdc7351774dbe18cfefc4d2aa3bb","tid":2192211,"uid":80827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T03:40:17.000Z","msg":"廠"},{"pid":"4bb6a63f160ac0ca055ebcaa6dfd50f2ce0b8154","tid":2192211,"uid":312333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T03:41:03.000Z","msg":"街"},{"pid":"16b31198b2504e6b4f81689f19fe02678dfdcd28","tid":2192211,"uid":58630,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T03:42:28.000Z","msg":"咁衰11有冇違反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39ab83280d92cc049600371f9eb88360e484a704","tid":2192211,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:07:24.000Z","msg":"呢條人渣"},{"pid":"8eee0f7d69220de3045b9e0566251fa475a078aa","tid":2192211,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:07:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVEGshQH.gif&amp;h=3d5d3567&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"ff7d7d57e24e470ab838cad25b8a76a132190c4a","tid":2192211,"uid":184726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:09:48.000Z","msg":"湯家驊認為搞細路非違反人權<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}